definitions.definition: Any culture whose values and lifestyles are opposed to those of the established mainstream culture , especially to Western culture.

main_definition: Any culture whose values and lifestyles are opposed to those of the established mainstream culture , especially to Western culture.

definitions.definition: A cultural movement most prominent in the 1960s and 1970s, associated with peace , free love and opposition to commercialism ; the hippie movement.

main_definition: A cultural movement most prominent in the 1960s and 1970s, associated with peace , free love and opposition to commercialism ; the hippie movement.
